@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName WenQuanYi Micro Hei
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam maxmessagesize 120
skinparam ParticipantPadding 40
skinparam BoxPadding 10

title 企业RAG — 登录流程

actor 用户 as User
participant "Vue 3 前端" as Browser
participant "UserController" as Ctrl
participant "RateLimitService" as RL
participant "UserService" as Svc
participant "AuthController" as AuthCtrl
database "MySQL\n(users 表)" as DB
database "Redis\n(Token 缓存)" as Redis

== 登录 ==

User -> Browser: 输入用户名、密码
Browser -> Ctrl: POST /api/v1/users/login\n{username, password}
Ctrl -> RL: checkLoginByIp(clientIp)
RL --> Ctrl: IP 速率检查通过
Ctrl -> Svc: authenticateUser(username, password)
Svc -> DB: SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE username = ?
DB --> Svc: user 实体 (含 BCrypt 哈希)
Svc -> Svc: PasswordUtil.matches(password, hash)
alt 密码匹配
    Svc -> Svc: jwtUtils.generateToken(username)\nclaims: userId, role, orgTags\n有效期 1 小时
    Svc -> Svc: jwtUtils.generateRefreshToken(username)\nclaims: type="refresh", userId\n有效期 7 天
    Svc -> Redis: SET token:{tokenId}\nvalue: userId\nEXPIRE 3600
    Redis --> Svc: OK
    Svc --> Ctrl: {token, refreshToken}
    Ctrl --> Browser: 200 {code:200, message, data:{token, refreshToken}}
    Browser -> Browser: localStorage.setItem\n('token', token)\n('refreshToken', refreshToken)
    Browser --> User: 跳转至原请求页面
else 密码不匹配
    Svc --> Ctrl: CustomException\n("Invalid credentials")
    Ctrl --> Browser: 401 {code:401, message:"Invalid credentials"}
    Browser --> User: 提示错误，留在登录页
else 速率限制触发
    RL --> Ctrl: RateLimitExceededException
    Ctrl --> Browser: 429 {code:429, retryAfterSeconds: N}
    Browser --> User: 提示稍后重试
end

== 获取用户信息 ==

Browser -> Ctrl: GET /api/v1/users/me\n(Authorization: Bearer token)
Ctrl -> Ctrl: jwtUtils.validateToken(token)\n提取 username
Ctrl -> DB: SELECT * FROM users\nWHERE username = ?
DB --> Ctrl: user (id, username, role, orgTags, primaryOrg)
Ctrl --> Browser: 200 {code:200, data:{id, userName, role, orgTags, primaryOrg}}
Browser -> Browser: 更新 authStore.userInfo

== Token 刷新 ==

note over Browser, Redis
  请求拦截器检测到 Token 即将过期 (剩余 < 5 分钟)
  或后端返回过期码 9999/9998/3333 时自动触发
end note
Browser -> AuthCtrl: POST /api/v1/auth/refreshToken\n{refreshToken}
AuthCtrl -> AuthCtrl: jwtUtils.validateRefreshToken\n验证 type="refresh" 声明
AuthCtrl -> Redis: isRefreshTokenValid(refreshTokenId)
Redis --> AuthCtrl: 有效
AuthCtrl -> AuthCtrl: generateToken(username)\n+ generateRefreshToken(username)\n双 Token 轮换
AuthCtrl --> Browser: 200 {code:200, data:{token, refreshToken}}
Browser -> Browser: 更新 localStorage\n重试原请求

== 登出 ==

User -> Browser: 点击退出登录
Browser -> Ctrl: POST /api/v1/users/logout\n(Authorization: Bearer token)
Ctrl -> Ctrl: jwtUtils.invalidateToken(token)\n加入 Redis 黑名单
Ctrl -> Redis: removeTokenFromCache(tokenId)
Ctrl --> Browser: 200 {code:200}
Browser -> Browser: clearAuthStorage\n(移除 token + refreshToken + userInfo)
Browser --> User: 跳转至登录页

@enduml
